values: 再；其他；另外；此外；否则；要不然

word_group.brief_definition: 或者；要么；要不然；否则；不然；否则将承担一切后果
别的东西；别的什么；别的事情
另外一件事, 别的东西
最重要的是；首先；除…之外
其他的呢；还有什么；除此之外呢
别的地方；其他地方；别处

bilingual.source: I couldn't see a dog or anything else.
bilingual.target: 我没看到狗或其他任何东西。

bilingual.source: The soundtrack is recorded before anything else is done.
bilingual.target: 配乐在其他任何事情之前录制。

bilingual.source: Papa, he says he doesn't want anything else from you.
bilingual.target: 爸爸，他说他不想要你其他的东西。

bilingual.source: He was tall, much taller than anyone else in the class.
bilingual.target: 他很高，比班里其他人都高得多。

bilingual.source: People wanted to know if lightning was really produced by electricity or something else.
bilingual.target: 人们想知道闪电是否真的由电产生或是其他东西。

bilingual.source: "Now that a great king has drunk from the cup, no one else should," she replied.
bilingual.target: “既然伟大的国王已经用过这个杯子，其他人就不该用了，”她回答道。

bilingual.source: It is extremely beautiful and you can experience the indigenous Australia there more than anywhere else.
bilingual.target: 那里非常美丽，你可以比在其他地方更多地体验到澳大利亚的原住民文化。

bilingual.source: "We allow students the special things they need to help them learn just as easily as everyone else," she replied.
bilingual.target: “我们允许学生使用他们需要的特殊物品，以帮助他们像其他人一样轻松学习，”她回答道。

list.abstract: else，英文单词，可作形容词、副词，翻译为别的、其他的、否则等。

yingyinNormal.en: He can't sit somewhere else?
yingyinNormal.zh: 他不能坐其他地方吗？

yingyinNormal.en: You have anyone to go to, any family anyplace else?
yingyinNormal.zh: 你有其他人可以求助，其他家庭或者地方可去吗？

yingyinNormal.en: How everyone else found out is a mystery to me.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我也想不通其他人是怎么知道的。

yingyinNormal.en: And they built something else as well, a brand.
yingyinNormal.zh: 他们还会建造其他的东西，一个品牌。

yingyinNormal.en: Oh! Where is everybody else? Ah, just me today.
yingyinNormal.zh: 喔! 那其他人呢? 额，今天只有我。

yingyinNormal.en: Everyone else in school will be your customers.
yingyinNormal.zh: 学校里的所有其他人则会成为你们的顾客。

yingyinNormal.en: Can you please paint something else now? Oh, you.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你现在能画点其他的东西吗？您真会开玩笑。

yingyinNormal.en: Hello? Hello? Hey, Charlie. Did anybody else hear?
yingyinNormal.zh: 嗨？嘿，查理，听说其他人的消息了吗？

yingyinNormal.en: Everybody else, be as gross as possible. Think dirty thoughts.
yingyinNormal.zh: 其他人尽可能搞脏这里，用肮脏的方法思维。

yingyinNormal.en: Master the bloomer, and everything else will fall into place.
yingyinNormal.zh: 掌握了这种面包的做法，那么其他的就不在话下。

yingyinNormal.en: Okay, I will find someplace else to do the rest of my appointments. I just don't know what the big deal is.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我会找其他地方来做我其他的客人，这有什么大不了的。

yingyinNormal.en: As far as everyone else is concerned, going to the Prime Minister and way beyond, Charles Augustus...
yingyinNormal.zh: 对于其他人来说，包括首相以及其他人，查尔斯·奥古斯塔斯...

yingyinNormal.en: The way you said it. It's like goodbye. Say something else.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你说得好像是在告别，说点其他的。

yingyinNormal.en: Does anyone else feel she should be moving in slow motion?
yingyinNormal.zh: 有其他人认为她应该以慢动作移动吗？

yingyinNormal.en: Because everybody else is. That's not the way I see it.
yingyinNormal.zh: 因为其他人都在成长啊。我觉得不是这样。

yingyinNormal.en: Do you ever look in the mirror and want to see someone else?
yingyinNormal.zh: 你有没有过照镜子时希望能看到其他人？

yingyinNormal.en: No. It had to have been someone else, someone from your crew.
yingyinNormal.zh: 不，肯定是其他人，你们那伙人中的一员。

yingyinNormal.en: Okay, 10. Okay, Monica picks 10. I call nine. Anyone else?
yingyinNormal.zh: 好喔，我选“十”。那我选“九”。还有其他的吗?

yingyinNormal.en: Now, somebody else is gonna want to make a bet on the outcome of their bet.
yingyinNormal.zh: 现在，有其他人想赌他们赌博的结果。

yingyinNormal.en: You two in charge of stealing food and the essentials. And nothing else.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你们两个去偷食物和必需品，其他都别拿。

direction_info.description:
数据源自2012-2023年12年间全国考研试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2012-2023年全国考研英语一和考研英语二共24套考研试卷，包括阅读、完型填空、翻译、写作等所有题型。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>
精选全国考研考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2012-2023年12年间全国考研英语一和考研英语二试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

word_family.mean: adv. 此外；其他；另外；不同的；作为替代；见下

examination_example.sentence: I truly believe that once you get that first word out everything <highlight>else</highlight> will just flow.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 我真的相信，一旦你说出第一个字，其他一切都会顺其自然地发生。

examination_example.sentence: We unconsciously associate fast food with speed and impatience and carry those impulses into whatever <highlight>else</highlight> we're doing.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 我们不自觉地将快餐与速度和不耐烦联系在一起，并将这些冲动带入我们正在做的其他事情中。

sense_info_list.en: used to introduce the second of two possibilities

examination_example.sentence: The flywheel of work-related thoughts keeps spinning — or <highlight>else</highlight> you're so exhausted that a challenging book's the last thing you need.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 与工作相关的思想飞轮不停旋转——或者你太累了，最不需要的就是一本有挑战性的书。

word_usage.usage: else作形容词时，通常放在who，what，which或者something，anything，nothing，anyone，everyone等词之后，修饰限定这些词，如：I don't want anything else；作副词时，通常放在when，where，how等词之后，如：Where else do you want to go？

word_family.mean: adv. 此外；其他；另外；不同的；作为替代；见下

examination_example.sentence: What <highlight>else</highlight> could be done to reduce fatal road accidents in addition to safer roads?
examination_example.sentence_trans: 除了更安全的道路外，还可以采取什么措施来减少致命的道路事故？

examination_example.sentence: The image of James Dean will be recreated on screen with his voice dubbed by someone <highlight>else</highlight>.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 詹姆斯·迪恩（James Dean）的形象将通过他人配音在屏幕上重现。

examination_example.sentence: The problem comes when everyone is using a navigation app which tells them to avoid everyone <highlight>else</highlight> using the same gadget.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 当每个人都在使用导航应用程序时，问题就来了，该应用程序告诉他们不要让其他人使用相同的设备。

word_usage.usage: else无比较级和最高级形式。
else的所有格形式是else's，但与someone或anyone连用时，应说someone else's，不能说someone's else。

examination_example.sentence: You can use me as a last resort (选择), and if nobody <highlight>else</highlight> volunteers, then I will do it.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 您可以把我作为最后的手段，如果没有其他志愿者，那么我将做这件事。

examination_example.sentence: I can't imagine doing anything <highlight>else</highlight> with my life.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 我无法想象这辈子还能做什么。

examination_example.sentence: Then that person does something nice for someone <highlight>else</highlight>.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 然后那个人为别人做了好事。

examination_example.sentence: What <highlight>else</highlight> can you do to improve your online studies?
examination_example.sentence_trans: 你还能做些什么来提高你的在线学习？

examination_example.sentence: Why did the father say that the girl would live as long as anyone <highlight>else</highlight>?
examination_example.sentence_trans: 为什么父亲说这个女孩会和其他人一样长寿？

examination_example.sentence: Southern Chinese buy just enough food for one meal or one day, or <highlight>else</highlight> the food may go bad.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 南方人买的食物只够吃一顿饭或者吃一天，否则食物会变质。
